headline: Amy E. Dahl Elected to the EMCOR Group, Inc. Board of Directors
summary: NORWALK, Conn., December 19, 2024--EMCOR Group, Inc. (the "Company") (NYSE: EME) announced today the election to the Company’s Board of Directors of Amy E. Dahl, effective December 18, 2024.
